<style>
  .nav-spacer {display: none;}
</style>

<div class="homebg">
  <div class="homebgoverlay">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pull-left" style="padding-top: 20px; color: #4fc090;">
      Welcome to our little "shop local" experiment - <span style="color: #fff;">It's free to use and non profit!</span>
    </div>
    <div class="pull-right home-nav">
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
  <li>
  <%= link_to('Logout', destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete) %>        
  </li>
<% else %>
  <%= link_to('Already Have An Account? Login', new_user_session_path)  %>  
<% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container" style="padding:100px 0;">
        <div class="row" style="background: none; box-shadow:none;">
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <img src="http://res.cloudinary.com/theblackandwhites/image/upload/v1501220372/tamborine_weekly/Logomakr_7NO21V.png" alt="Tamborine Weekly" width="300">
            <h1>Join our little "shop local" experiment!</h1>
            <h4>Being able to call Tamborine Mountain home is very special to me. However, I drive down the mountain every week to purchase tasteless, overpriced produce from the big super markets only to pass dozens of fruit trees, vege patches and roadside stalls on the way home. So I thought it would be a great opportunity to launch a new initiative for the community.</h4><br />
            <h4>Introducing, Tamborine Weekly!</h4><br />
            <p style="font-size: 16px;">This non profit site means that all Tamborine Mountain locals can sell and purchase left over produce to and from their neighbours. The process is all cash in hand and very easy to use.</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Sign up for your free account</li>
              <li>If you're selling, set up your stall and add your products</li>
              <li>Browse and add products to your cart</li>
              <li>Generate your shopping list</li>
              <li>Go pick up and pay for your items</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="form-box">
              <h2>Sign up it's free and takes a few seconds to get started.</h2>
              <br />

              <%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
                <%= devise_error_messages! %>

                <div class="form-group float-label-control">
                  <%= f.label :first_name %>
                  <%= f.text_field :first_name, autofocus: true, placeholder: "First Name", class: "form-control", :required => true %>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group float-label-control">
                  <%= f.label :last_name %>
                  <%= f.text_field :last_name, placeholder: "Last Name", class: "form-control", :required => true %>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group float-label-control">
                  <%= f.label :email %>
                  <%= f.email_field :email, placeholder: "Your Email", class: "form-control" %>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group float-label-control">
                  <%= f.label :password %>
       
                  <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off", placeholder: "Password", class: "form-control" %>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group float-label-control">
                  <%= f.label :password_confirmation %>
                  <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "off", placeholder: "Confirm Password" %>
                </div>

                <div class="actions">
                  <%= f.submit "Create your account", class: "btn btn-lg btn-success" %>
                </div>
              <% end %>
              <br>
              <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="myfooter" style="color: #fff; position: absolute; z-index: 3; width: 100%; padding: 20px; background-color: #14171e; bottom: 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pull-left">This experiment was designed by small business marketing consultant <a href="https://www.theblackandwhites.com.au" target="_blank" style="color: #4fc090">The Black &amp; Whites</a></div>
    <div class="pull-right">Copyright 2017 - All rights reserved.</div>
  </div>
</div>